voyage in 2000 in Berkeley, California.</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<p>Prior to retiring from the corporate world to teach capoeira professionally, Zumbi was a business development manager at SK Telecom. Zumbi graduated from the Wharton School with an MBA in Marketing. He credits his disciplined training and beloved Capoeira community as major contributors to his professional and academic success.</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<p>Please learn more about Professor Zumbi through the following news articles and blog posts:</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/zumbicdo/videos/vb.167459899952376/976138475751177/?type=2&theater\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/z-whiteicon-57x57px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi on EBS News\" /></a><p> EBS News 2015<p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mbn.co.kr/player/movieContents.mbn?content_cls_cd=20&content_id=1046234&autoPlay=true&captionMotion=true&controlbarMotion=true&useThumbnail=true&setMenualQuality=360&relay_type=1&isIframe=true&width=555&height=312\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/z-whiteicon-57x57px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi on MBN\" /></a><p> MBN 2013<p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JmstTp-uggI\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/z-whiteicon-57x57px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi and Red Bull\" /></a><p> Red Bull Korea 2012<p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://hoperecov.blog.me/130184476207\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/z-whiteicon-57x57px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi in Blogs\" /></a><p> Minji\'s Blog<p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-5\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<a href=\"http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20120828000982&cpv=0\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/z-whiteicon-57x57px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi in the Korea Herald\" /></a><p> The Korea Herald 2012<p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20110920000742\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/z-whiteicon-57x57px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi in the Korea Herald\" /></a><p> The Korea Herald 2011<p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.lgchallengers.com/leadership/other_challenge/air/\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/z-whiteicon-57x57px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi and SK Telecom\" /></a><p> LG Challengers Interview 2011<p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/zumbicdo/videos/10151001181204540/\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/z-whiteicon-57x57px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi and SK Telecom\" /></a><p> SK Telecom GBS 2010<p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n</div> \r\n\r\n</div>\";s:15:\"section_title_2\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"section_title_color_2\";s:7:\"#ff8800\";s:28:\"section_title_border_color_2\";s:7:\"#000000\";s:23:\"section_content_color_2\";s:7:\"#ff8800\";s:16:\"section_anchor_2\";s:20:\"section-introduction\";s:20:\"section_background_2\";a:5:{s:5:\"color\";s:7:\"#000000\";s:5:\"image\";s:61:\"http://www.zumbicdo.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:8:\"position\";s:8:\"top left\";s:10:\"attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";}s:17:\"background_size_2\";s:3:\"yes\";s:12:\"full_width_2\";s:3:\"yes\";s:19:\"section_css_class_2\";s:20:\"section-introduction\";s:17:\"section_content_2\";s:2617:\"<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Are you an ambitious student or young profession with any of the following characteristics?</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Interested in music and dance</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate about learning languages</li>\r\n	<li>Interested in cultural experiences</li>\r\n	<li>Wanting improved balance and flexibility</li>\r\n	<li>Seriously committed to health &amp; fitness</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Learn with Professor Zumbi today!</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn btn-default btn-lg\" href=\"#section-introduction\">Free Class</a></p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/desafio-2014-artwork-150x150px.png\" alt=\"Desafio 2014 Art\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<div class=\"ot-content\">\r\n<h4 class=\"ot-title\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/suingue-mandingado4-150x150px.png\" alt=\"suingue mandingado\" /></h4>\r\n<h4 class=\"ot-title\" style=\"text-align: right;\">What is Capoeira?</h4>\r\n<h5 class=\"ot-title\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Capoeira is a game.</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">To learn to play Capoeira is to embark on a voyage. Once you set sail you are called a <em>Capoeirista</em>. Capoeira is endless. So you will need a navigator to guide you. That\'s where your Capoeira teacher comes in. With Professor Zumbi you can ensure that your Capoeira experience has set sail for the intersection of:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Art (<i class=\"fa fa-check\"> </i>)</li>\r\n	<li>Discipline (<i class=\"fa fa-check\"> </i>)</li>\r\n	<li>Strategy (<i class=\"fa fa-check\"> </i>)</li>\r\n	<li>Philosophy (<i class=\"fa fa-check\"> </i>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p style=\"color: #000;\"><a href=\"http://www.capoeirastudio.com\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n<i class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right\"> </i> www.capoeirastudio.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";s:15:\"section_title_3\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"section_title_color_3\";s:7:\"#305999\";s:28:\"section_title_border_color_3\";s:7:\"#305999\";s:23:\"section_content_color_3\";s:7:\"#ff8800\";s:16:\"section_anchor_3\";s:18:\"section-activities\";s:20:\"section_background_3\";a:5:{s:5:\"color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:8:\"position\";s:13:\"center center\";s:10:\"attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";}s:17:\"background_size_3\";s:3:\"yes\";s:12:\"full_width_3\";s:2:\"no\";s:19:\"section_css_class_3\";s:18:\"section-activities\";s:17:\"section_content_3\";s:2380:\"<div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<h1>ACTIVITIES</h1>\r\nSince moving to Korea in 2009, Professor Zumbi has been active in developing the local Capoeira community. His duties presently include:\r\n\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 \">\r\n<div class=\"service-box\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/capoeirastudio-icon-105x105px.png\" alt=\"capoeira studio\" />\r\n<h3>Capoeira Studio</h3>\r\nThe community of teachers and students at the Capoeira Studio are focused on improving strength, flexibility, agility, balance, concentration, rhythm, and quality of life through the creative and beautiful movement of the Afro-Brazilian artform called Capoeira.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.capoeirastudio.com\">Read More&gt;&gt;</a>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 \">\r\n<div class=\"service-box\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/capoeira-tricking-icon-105x105px.png\" alt=\"Capoeira Tricking\" />\r\n<h3>Capoeira Tricking</h3>\r\nProfessor Zumbi and Master Han join forces to teach Capoeira sequences with a focus on acrobatics. Prior experience with Capoeira or Tricking is required. Classes are held in Wangsimni on Sunday evenings. Annual members only.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.capoeirastudio.com\">Read More&gt;&gt;</a>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 \">\r\n<div class=\"service-box\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/cdo-logo-105x105px-2.png\" alt=\"cdo seoul\" />\r\n<h3>Suingue Mandingado</h3>\r\nEvery year Professor Zumbi and his students organize two events: Suingue Mandingado (a \"batizado\" where students are graded and given a Capoeira cord) and Desafio dos Mandingueiros (an \"encounter\" with selected Capoeira teachers).\r\n\r\n<a href=\"#\">Read More&gt;&gt;</a>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";s:15:\"section_title_4\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"section_title_color_4\";s:7:\"#ff8800\";s:28:\"section_title_border_color_4\";s:7:\"#ff8800\";s:23:\"section_content_color_4\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:16:\"section_anchor_4\";s:11:\"section-faq\";s:20:\"section_background_4\";a:5:{s:5:\"color\";s:7:\"#000000\";s:5:\"image\";s:88:\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/zumba-fadeblack.png\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:8:\"position\";s:12:\"bottom right\";s:10:\"attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";}s:17:\"background_size_4\";s:2:\"no\";s:12:\"full_width_4\";s:2:\"no\";s:19:\"section_css_class_4\";s:11:\"section-faq\";s:17:\"section_content_4\";s:2185:\"<div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<h1>FAQ</h1>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p style=\"color: #ff8800;\">What does \"Professor\" mean?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is a Portuguese word meaning teacher. The title is bestowed upon an \"instrutor\" (or a student that provides instruction to other students) that has attained a level of proficiency in the teaching of Capoeira to beginners and advanced students. Zumbi was awarded the title of professor in 2015 from Mestre Chicote, a very famous Capoeira master from Brazil that now teaches in Europe. Professor Zumbi received his professor cord in the presence of Capoeira grand masters, Mestre Suassuna and Mestre Acordeon.</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: #ff8800;\">What does \"Zumbi\" mean?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zumbi (1655 - November 20, 1695), also known as Zumbi dos Palmares, was the last of the leaders of the Quilombo dos Palmares, in the present-day state of Alagoas, Brazil. [source: Wikipedia]</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: #ff8800;\">What does \"CDO\" mean?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CDO stands for Cordão de Ouro which was the name given to a legendary fighter in Brazil. It is also the name of Zumbi\'s capoeira group, the capoeira group started by Mestre Suassuna, a legend himself.</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: #ff8800;\">How can I contact Zumbi?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Send a message via <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/zumbicdo\">Facebook</a> to register for workshops / classes or just say hi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\";s:15:\"section_title_5\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"section_title_color_5\";s:7:\"#ff8c00\";s:28:\"section_title_border_color_5\";s:7:\"#ff6c00\";s:23:\"section_content_color_5\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:16:\"section_anchor_5\";s:17:\"section-quotation\";s:20:\"section_background_5\";a:5:{s:5:\"color\";s:7:\"#ff8800\";s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:8:\"position\";s:8:\"top left\";s:10:\"attachment\";s:6:\"scroll\";}s:17:\"background_size_5\";s:2:\"no\";s:12:\"full_width_5\";s:2:\"no\";s:19:\"section_css_class_5\";s:17:\"section-quotation\";s:17:\"section_content_5\";s:369:\"<div style=\"text-align: center; font-family: \'Syncopate\';\">\r\n<h1>\"There was no reason to stay in Seoul.. But now... I don\'t wanna leave Seoul. Only because of Professor Zumbi\'s Capoeira class!!!\"</h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Rosa, <a style=\"color: #000000; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.capoeirastudio.com/\">Capoeira Studio</a> Student</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\";s:15:\"section_title_6\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"section_title_color_6\";s:7:\"#ff8800\";s:28:\"section_title_border_color_6\";s:7:\"#ff8800\";s:23:\"section_content_color_6\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:16:\"section_anchor_6\";s:18:\"section-promotions\";s:20:\"section_background_6\";a:5:{s:5:\"color\";s:7:\"#000000\";s:5:\"image\";s:88:\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/zumba-fadeblack.png\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:8:\"position\";s:12:\"bottom right\";s:10:\"attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";}s:17:\"background_size_6\";s:2:\"no\";s:12:\"full_width_6\";s:2:\"no\";s:19:\"section_css_class_6\";s:17:\"section-promotion\";s:17:\"section_content_6\";s:1185:\"<div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<h1>FREE CLASSES</h1>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ready to try something new? Experience the joys and challenges of group Capoeira classes.\r\nSome prior athletic ability required.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn btn-default btn-lg\" style=\"text-align: center;\" href=\"http://www.capoeirastudio.com\">Free Trial Class</a></p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Design your ideal Capoeira workout with Professor Zumbi and get kicking today.\r\nNo athletic ability required.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn btn-default btn-lg\" style=\"text-align: center;\" href=\"tel://010-9090-9183\">Free Private Class</a></p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\";s:15:\"section_title_7\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"section_title_color_7\";s:0:\"\";s:28:\"section_title_border_color_7\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"section_content_color_7\";s:7:\"#000000\";s:16:\"section_anchor_7\";s:15:\"section-reviews\";s:20:\"section_background_7\";a:5:{s:5:\"color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:8:\"position\";s:8:\"top left\";s:10:\"attachment\";s:6:\"scroll\";}s:17:\"background_size_7\";s:2:\"no\";s:12:\"full_width_7\";s:2:\"no\";s:19:\"section_css_class_7\";s:15:\"section-reviews\";s:17:\"section_content_7\";s:4162:\"<div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<h1>REVIEWS</h1>\r\n<p style=\"color: #ff8800\">Here is what Professor Zumbi\'s students had to say about him, his group (<a href=\"http://www.cdoseoul.com\" target=\"_new\">Cordão de Ouro Seoul</a>), and his academy (<a href=\"http://www.capoeirastudio.com\" target=\"_new\">the Capoeira Studio</a>) in their respective languages.</p>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img width=\"100px\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/graduado-king-386x386px.png\" alt=\"King\" /><h3>KING</h3><p>음악,춤,무술,자유와 사람이 있는곳... 자신을 표현하는 다양한 방법이 한데 어우러져 있어 생활의 활력소가 되기에 충분한 \'카포에라\'를 하고있는 요즘 전 하루하루가 너무 즐겁습니다.^^ </p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img width=\"100px\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/tigresa-595x595px.png\" alt=\"Tiger\" /><h3>TIGRESA</h3><p>스튜디오에 들어서는 순간, 또 다른 세상이 펼쳐집니다. 17세기 아프리카의 정취부터 20세기 초 브라질 바히아의 열기까지.... 화려한 기술이 눈을 사로잡고, 신나는 음악이 귀를 사로잡을 것입니다. 도전해 보세요! 카포에라가 지금 여러분을 기다리고 있습니다!!!</p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img width=\"100px\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/verde-543x543px.png\" alt=\"Verde\" /><h3>COBRA VERDE</h3><p>CDO Seoul is more than a gym to exercise in, or a class to learn from, it\'s a family that will support you for as long as you are staying in Korea, and will continue to be a part of your life long after you leave. <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/eric.follows/posts/10203292166743729:0\" target=\"_new\" />Read More&gt;&gt;</a></p></div>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img width=\"100px\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/segredo-451x451px.png\" alt=\"Segredo\" /><h3>SEGREDO DA LUA</h3><p>택견, 무에타이, 복싱.. 많은 운동을 해보았지만 카포에라는 사람들과 어울려 음악과 춤, 무술을 동시에 즐길 수 있어 더욱 오래 즐기면서 할 수 있는 것 같습니다! 자신에게 맞는 운동을 찾지 못 해 이것 저것 많이 해본 분들이라면 꼭 한 번쯤 해보길 권하고 싶네요 :)</p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img width=\"100px\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/bubbles-369x369px.png\" alt=\"Bubbles\" /><h3>CHAMPANHE</h3><p>카포에라처럼 전신을 다 사용하면서 즐겁게 하는 무술은 없는 것 같아요! 댄스, 아크로바틱, 아프로-브라질악기, 노래까지~ 다양한 장르의 훈련을 한꺼번에 할 수 있는 카포에라 정말 매력있답니다. 몸에 흥을 타고 나셨거나 몸을 가만히 두는 것을 못하신다면... 당신도 카포에라리스타가 될 수 있을 거에요! 한번 도전해 보세요^^</p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img width=\"100px\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/garça-570x570px.png\" alt=\"Garça\" /><h3>GARÇA</h3><p>Capoeira ist mehr als nur Sport. Es besteht aus Musik, Tanzen, Singen, Akrobatik und vor allem - Gemeinschaft und Respekt. CDO Seoul gibt mir das Gefühl, eine Familie in Südkorea zu haben. Gerade in meinem stressigen Berufsleben hat mir CDO Seoul und Zumbi (Trainer) mir einen wunderbaren Ort zum abschalten, mit Freude(n) und der Kreativität geschaffen. Es lohnt sich einfach mal vorbei zu kommen!!</p></div>\r\n<img style=\"max-height: 5px;\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/spacer.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\";s:15:\"section_title_8\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"section_title_color_8\";s:0:\"\";s:28:\"section_title_border_color_8\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"section_content_color_8\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:16:\"section_anchor_8\";s:14:\"section-donate\";s:20:\"section_background_8\";a:5:{s:5:\"color\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";s:120:\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/10958943_1009240749103904_2577027696725228395_o.jpg\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:8:\"position\";s:13:\"center center\";s:10:\"attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";}s:17:\"background_size_8\";s:3:\"yes\";s:12:\"full_width_8\";s:2:\"no\";s:19:\"section_css_class_8\";s:14:\"section-donate\";s:17:\"section_content_8\";s:520:\"<div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p class=\"ot-under\">Do you like what Professor Zumbi has been doing? Why not make a donation?</p>\r\n<a href=\"#\">\r\n<img width=\"200px\" src=\"http://zumbicdo.quilombolaengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/zumbcdo-inverted-icon-550x550px.png\" alt=\"Zumbi CDO\" />\r\